SUBENT        41557003   20260112   20260319   20260319       4226
BIB                  6         15
REACTION   (96-CM-248(0,F)ELEM/MASS,IND,FY)
           Xe isotopes absolute yields .
ANALYSIS    Cumulative yield of Xe-138 was used to define absolute
           independent yields of Xe isotopes. Xe-138 fractional
           cumulative yield of 0.70 +- 0.15 was used from known
           systematics of K.F.Flynn+, A.C.Wahl+ :
REL-REF    (R,,K.F.Flynn+,J,JIN,39,759,1977)
           (R,,A.C.Wahl+,J,AND,39,(1),1,1988)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Type of uncertainty is not explained in the
           article.
STATUS     (TABLE,,Yu.P.Gangrskii,J,PPN/L,2,92,2005) Table 2.
           (DEP,41557002)
HISTORY    (20141229A) ANALYSIS free text was corrected:
            "fraction" -> "fractional cumulative yield"
           according to the comment of S.Simakov (NDS,IAEA).
ENDBIB              15
